{"tid":2060859,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［初選］沒有大台只有平台 — 由連登投票，大眾跟隨","createTime":"2020-06-12T03:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T05:25:40.000Z","uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"238090e0426c1516f561ace8bf8d0ab0c199af7f","tid":2060859,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T03:16:38.000Z","msg":"老老柒柒，見到戴耀庭個初選搞到一鑊泡<br />\n民主党又唔肯簽承諾，到時肯定又縮<br />\n<br />\n唔想比泛民襲斷，又唔想比熱狗執雞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不如由連登投票，市民跟隨結果去投票</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>理由</ins></span><br />\n1. 現實投票，本土素人難宣傳，市民難了解/跟唔貼，盲目相信戴教授/泛民。<br />\n反而連登仔跟得比較緊，對素人了解較大眾深，而<span style=\"color: gold;\">市民既然只想跟大隊，與其跟泛民，不如跟連登。</span>（有戴教授endorse更好）<br />\n<br />\n2. 連登就算有5毛/泛民/熱狗打手，<span style=\"color: gold;\">運動主流意見依然係佔會員大多數</span>，好多行動post/攬炒巴嘅post都過千正皮，甚至幾千，相信用正負皮投票可以得到可信服結果<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>實行方式</ins></span><br />\n0. 跟據戴教授初選名單，有意參與初選者為候選人<br />\n<br />\n1. 一post一個候選人，以#1 正負皮為準<br />\n#1 會簡介候選人<span style=\"color: red;\">立場、政績、事件</span><br />\n<br />\n2. P牌問題：無得投票，可以留言表態<br />\n（討論方向：會唔會逐個count返當票數？<br />\na. 為免5毛入攝，可先起底，有證據證明為5毛則cap圖做證當<span style=\"color: blue;\">廢票</span><br />\nb. 為免5毛用新acc刷數據，劃死2020年1月1日前/某日子前 嘅P牌先納入<span style=\"color: green;\">有效P牌票</span>）<br />\n以上都可以再作討論<br />\n<br />\n3. 35+配票方法：有idea但係唔穿橋住<br />\n<br />\n4. 如果連登比人ddos點算，轉場，到時再算<br />\n<br />\n5. 選出正式參選名單，可籌組新政黨？（可討論）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果覺得可行，麻煩推上熱門</span><br />\n<br />\n投票<span style=\"color: gold;\">搞手</span>由可信性較高會員準備更有說服力，<br />\n當然希望攬炒團隊可以接手搞，不過知道國際線都好忙；<br />\n個人都有心水會員，不過都睇連登仔意見<br />\n<br />\n好清楚35+係不可能任務，但係唔代表要將資源拱手相讓，<span style=\"color: gold;\">能力範盡自己最大努力先係香港人精神</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nKFHG SDKM"},{"pid":"3dbbfc83a662b5b9b0d5c74eed4a4fc03f639617","tid":2060859,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T03:22:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c83d50cd1286a6659467ac8df79de9df1ceb9169","tid":2060859,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T03:22:41.000Z","msg":"明知不可為而為之<br />\n<br />\n香港人反抗"},{"pid":"dfcc1652a3c33d514e4e298bdbc7091b8769977b","tid":2060859,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T03:29:05.000Z","msg":"咁快有兩個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05399a9fe1e4f84fa947b286b2df3c37941c206d","tid":2060859,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T03:29:49.000Z","msg":"612 一周年"},{"pid":"8b30f390727f6bbd38a31b3703b707b247abb60f","tid":2060859,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T03:35:04.000Z","msg":"kfhg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光gwong1 <br />\n重新開post 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2038217a0f80df0591609675e7976082250c4a","tid":2060859,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b30f390727f6bbd38a31b3703b707b247abb60f","tid":2060859,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T03:35:04.000Z","msg":"kfhg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光gwong1 <br />\n重新開post 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T03:40:58.000Z","msg":"屌 係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自膠先<img src=\"/assets/f